value.name: beginNode_0
value.text: Welcome to Disney World ${subject} family! We know you just arrived but we need your help...

value.name: missionNode_1
value.text: ${charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0].name} is missing and we need ${himHerIt(charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0])} for our big party tonight, said ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name}. Will you help us find ${himHerIt(charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0])}? Why donâ€™t you head towards ${pages[2].location.name} and look for clues along the way, you never know what you may find!

value.name: seekNode_2
value.text: Before you depart on your quest, you must eat to gain strength. While eating you think that maybe someone in ${pages[3].location.name} will know where ${charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0].name} went...

value.name: seekNode_3
value.text: Great Job! it looks like you found ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name} in ${page.location.name}! Maybe ${heSheIt(charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0])} can help? Can you find any clues?

value.name: seekNode_4
value.text: I have no idea where ${charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0].name} could be, said ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name}, but maybe you should go to ${pages[6].location.name}, they have all sorts of cool things that might be able to track ${himHerIt(charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0])} down!

value.name: seekNode_5
value.text: On your way to ${pages[6].location.name}, you meet ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name}, but ${heSheIt(charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0])} didn't see ${charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0].name} either. You keep looking...

value.name: seekNode_6
value.text: Arriving at ${page.location.name} you run into ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name}. ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name} remembered that ${charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0].name} was attending ${pages[8].location.name} that afternoon.

value.name: seekNode_7
value.text: In fact, ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name} has just left ${pages[8].location.name}. The gathering at ${pages[8].location.name} is over, ${heSheIt(charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0])} says, but maybe ${charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0].name} is still there? Why donâ€™t you ask ${charactersByGroup(pages[8],'disney')[0].name}? ${heSheIt(charactersByGroup(pages[8],'disney')[0])} was there too!

value.name: seekNode_8
value.text: When you reach ${page.location.name} you see ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name}, who gladly lets you hop on ${himHerIt(charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0])} back to help the search. The fastest way to travel around Disney World is with me, shouts ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name}, as you both take off towards the castle.

value.name: seekNode_9
value.text: In front of the castle you find a crowd of people. Suddenly, music starts playing and you find yourself in the middle of a parade!

value.name: endNode_10
value.text:
Inside the crowd you suddenly see ${charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0].name}! ${heSheIt(charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0])} is so happy to see you. 
${charactersByGroup(pages[1],'disney')[0].name} has told me all about your quest, ${heSheIt(charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0])} says, I'm so glad you have finally found me! 
To celebrate this, ${heSheIt(charactersByGroup(page,'disney')[0])} announces happily: Ladies and gentlemen, please welcome ${subject}, our special guests for tonight!

value.name: fireworksNode_11
value.text: As the day turns into night, ${charactersByGroup(pages[10],'disney')[0].name} magically lights the castle to add one last special touch to a very special day.
